If you are using the new atmk2004 Kurucz/Castelli 

http://kurucz.harvard.edu/papers/uppsala/

ODFNEW = as NOVER but with newly computed ODFs with better opacities
         and better abundances.
CASTELLI 2004 New grids of ATLAS9 model atmospheres (Castelli and Kurucz)
              arXiv:astro-ph/0405087 

         **THESE ARE THE PREFERRED MODELS**
 
         ***  4 Nov 2008 ALL A*ODFNEW.DAT FILES REPLACED ***
         ***   45000, 4.5 INSERTED INSTEAD OF DUPLICATE 45000, 5  ***

You NEED TO CHANGE KTTAU to 5 (NOT 3)

(there are more Teff values in the updated tables, and the length
of the Teff vector is hardcoded)

